Privacy Policy for Word Scramble Classic

Introduction
Welcome to Word Scramble Classic! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile game. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a safe gaming experience for all users.
Developer Information
Developer: [Fun Game Portal]
Contact Email: karamtariq007@gmail.com
Information We Collect
Information You Provide to Us
Game Progress: We store your game progress, scores, achievements, and unlocked levels locally on your device
Feedback: If you contact us for support or provide feedback, we may collect your email address and correspondence
Information Collected Automatically
Device Information: Device type, operating system version, unique device identifiers
Game Analytics: Gameplay statistics, levels completed, time spent playing
Performance Data: Crash reports, performance metrics to improve game functionality
Advertising ID: If you choose to watch rewarded videos, we may access your device's advertising identifier
Information We Do NOT Collect
Personal Identifiable Information: We do not collect names, addresses, phone numbers, or email addresses unless you voluntarily provide them for support
Location Data: We do not collect or access your precise location
Financial Information: We do not collect payment information (all transactions are handled by app store platforms)
Photos/Videos: We do not access your camera, photos, or videos
Contacts: We do not access your address book or contact list
How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
Game Functionality: To provide and maintain the game's core features
Progress Tracking: To save and restore your game progress
Improvement: To analyze game performance and improve user experience
Customer Support: To respond to your inquiries and provide assistance
Analytics: To understand game usage patterns and optimize gameplay
Advertising: To serve relevant ads if you choose to watch rewarded videos
Data Storage and Security
Local Storage: Most game data is stored locally on your device
Encryption: All data transmissions use industry-standard encryption
Security Measures: We implement reasonable security measures to protect against unauthorized access
Data Retention: We retain game data only as long as necessary to provide the service
Third-Party Services
We may use the following third-party services:
Analytics Providers: To understand game usage (data is anonymized)
Ad Networks: To serve rewarded video ads (only if you choose to watch them)
These third parties are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information and are prohibited from using it for any purpose other than providing services to us.
Children's Privacy
Our game is suitable for all ages and complies with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA):
No Age Gate Required: We do not collect personal information that would require parental consent
Educational Content: The game focuses on vocabulary building and educational value
Safe Environment: We provide a safe, ad-appropriate environment for children
Parental Controls: Parents can contact us to request deletion of any inadvertently collected information
Your Rights and Choices
You have the following rights regarding your information:
Access: You can request access to any personal information we hold about you
Correction: You can request correction of inaccurate information
Deletion: You can request deletion of your game data
Opt-out: You can opt-out of analytics collection in game settings
Data Portability: You can request a copy of your game data
Data Deletion
You can delete your game data at any time:
Contact Us: Email us to request complete data deletion
Uninstall: Uninstalling the game removes local data from your device
International Data Transfers
We process data in accordance with applicable laws including:
GDPR Compliance: For users in the European Union
CCPA Compliance: For users in California
COPPA Compliance: For users under 13 years of age
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time:
Notification: We will notify you of significant changes through the game
Review: We encourage you to review this policy periodically
Continued Use: Your continued use of the game after changes constitutes acceptance
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us:
Email: [karamtariq007@gmail.com
Response Time: We aim to respond to all inquiries within 48 hours
For users in the European Union, you also have the right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.
Consent
By using Word Scramble Classic, you consent to the collection and use of information as described in this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with any part of this policy, please discontinue use of our game.
